          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If the menu item has multiple images associated with it (to indicate any of the available states: on, off, or mixed), this property contains the width of the largest image. You can set the state images for a menu item using the setOnStateImage:, setOffStateImage:, and setMixedStateImage: methods of "
